  <!-- ── Synopsys ── -->
  <h2 id="synopsys">Synopsys</h2>

  <p>Dolphin Centrifuge designed and manufactured a complete Yellow Grease purification centrifuge system featuring an <a href="/disc-stack-centrifuge/">Alfa Laval 'Self-Cleaning' Disc-Centrifuge</a>. We supplied the system to a Used Cooking Oil (UCO) collection company. The following is a case study of this particular application of a Yellow Grease centrifuge for large-scale processing.</p>

  <!-- ── Case Study ── -->
  <h2 id="case-study">Case Study of Centrifuge on Yellow Grease Processing.</h2>

