  <h3 id="customer-background">Customer Background</h3>

  <p>A large-scale, mid-west waste oil collection company processed 6M gallons per year. They collect waste oil consisting of grease trap waste, UCO, yellow grease, restaurant slop oil, fryer oil, etc.</p>

  <p>The company used the age-old heating method and settling to get good oil from their collected yellow grease. In this process, the processor heats the yellow grease and allows it to settle under gravity. They then decant the clean oil off the top, leaving the 'rag layer' (emulsion), water, and sludge in the tank.</p>

  <h3 id="processing-challenges">Disadvantages of Heating and Settling</h3>

  <p>There are many challenges with the <strong>Heating &amp; Settling</strong> method of purifying yellow grease. Some of these are listed below.</p>

  <ul>
    <li>Settling under gravity takes time &ndash; it is a slow process.</li>
    <li>Settling also requires storage volume &ndash; more investment in tanks.</li>
    <li>Heating large volumes of crude yellow grease is energy-intensive.</li>
    <li>Decanting clean oil leaves a lot of 'good' oil in the tank bottom.</li>
    <li>Cleaning tank bottoms are essential to reclaiming storage volume.</li>
    <li>Disposal costs are associated with a large volume of tank bottom waste.</li>
  </ul>

  <h3 id="centrifuge-selection">Centrifuge Selection and Validation Process</h3>

  <p>The yellow grease company contacted Dolphin Centrifuge in mid-2018. They wanted to investigate using an <a href="/industrial-centrifuge/">industrial centrifuge</a> to improve their process efficiency.</p>

  <p>The customer provided a detailed process flow diagram (PFD) to Dolphin Centrifuge. The PFD provided details on their existing facility, equipment, and process.</p>

  <figure>
    <img
      src="/images/yellow-grease-purification-centrifuge/wvo-purifying-industrial-centrifuge.webp"
      alt="Industrial disc centrifuge processing yellow grease (WVO) at 40 GPM for large-scale UCO purification"
      width="800"
      height="450"
      loading="lazy"
      class="img-cap-800"
    />
    <figcaption>Centrifuge for water and WVO separation from yellow grease</figcaption>
